snippet.title: [MAME] Pastel Island (prototype) (c)1993 Visco
snippet.description: thanks to Shoutime for this, will be supported in 0.205 (the Xmas / Boxing Day release)  Makes heavy use of the SSV features I implemented over the 0.204-0.205 cycle (and then a few more on top of that)  The shadows aren't quite right, but otherwise emulation is working well.
